# CashBall Skills — Quick Reference
# 
# 3 auditing/validation tools for optimizing the project:
#
# 1. 🎮 Game State Audit
#    Server-side: validates game DB integrity, budgets, squads, contracts
#    Usage: cd server && npm run audit:gamestate <ROOM_CODE>
#    Docs: server/scripts/README.md, SKILLS.md
#
# 2. 🔌 Socket.io Event Contract Validator
#    Server-side: validates Socket.io events, detects orphaned handlers/emitters
#    Usage: cd server && npm run audit:socketio
#    Output: server/socketEventRegistry.json (event map)
#    Docs: server/scripts/README.md, SKILLS.md
#
# 3. 🎨 Frontend JSDoc Type Checker
#    Client-side: validates JSDoc types in React components
#    Usage: cd client && npm run check:types
#    Docs: client/scripts/README.md, SKILLS.md
#
# 📖 Full documentation: SKILLS.md
#
# Quick workflow:
#   1. Touch Socket.io? → npm run audit:socketio
#   2. Touch React? → npm run check:types
#   3. After matchday? → npm run audit:gamestate TEST-ROOM
#
